description:
Well the party is winding down. Slowly people are filtering out, and the haze and the buzz starts to set in. Rod Daily has already abandoned the festivities and decided on a late night shower. Mason Star has been partaking in the revelry, but as the action has petered out, he has come to the back of the house in search of a restroom and maybe something extra. When he sees Rod's chiseled frame in the shower, he immediately forgets about taking a piss, and instead focuses on trying to drain another vein.

Enjoy!
title: Private Party
